# Simple Sigma Detection Rules
# Rule: T1003.001 - LSASS Credential Dump
# Author: Philip Zangara
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1003.001 - OS Credential Dumping: LSASS Memory
# Generated from Sigma rule using sigma-cli with splunk_windows + splunk_sysmon_acceleration pipeline
# Note: filter_legitimate excludes lsass.exe spawned by wininit.exe (normal Windows boot behavior)
# Usage: Paste into Splunk search bar or save as a saved search

CommandLine="*lsass*" OR Image IN ("*\\mimikatz.exe", "*\\procdump.exe", "*\\procdump64.exe", "*\\wce.exe", "*\\pwdump.exe", "*\\lsadump.exe") NOT (Image="*\\lsass.exe" ParentImage="*\\wininit.exe")